			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="3635">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>I have been following <a href="/article/3141">Peg Staley&rsquo;s letters</a> over the months and have been impressed by her beauty and openness and her faith in her search. She touched home, as my mother had breast cancer in the early 60&rsquo;s. Happily, she is still with us. Though Peg is not, physically that is, I feel the glow of her spirit.</p>

<p>I cried upon reading of her last days. Thank you so much for publishing <strong>all</strong> of the letters. They mean so much to me and my family.</p>

<p>I know Peg&rsquo;s strength is best served through another medium not on this plane.</p>

<p>Much love to all of you.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Crystal Colgin<br>Boone, N.C.</p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

